reviews.text: Studio City at Macao is very big hotel and resort with shopping malls, restaurants, casino, entertainment shows, giant wheel, etc. As per the name the concept of construction is like cinema studio and theme. The batman show was exceptional. The hotel rooms are very good.

Nice, very large rooms, excellent buffet breakfast, magic show was a highlight! Not convenient to other locations, so walking to historic Taipa Village isn’t realistic. Shuttle buses are provided to limited locations. It was relaxing to stay there and the function rooms are very nice.

An amazing complex, luxury but affordable. There are numerous restaurants, bars, shops and entertainment options. I loved Batman show and golden reel. There is a discount if you book more than one entertainment shows the same day.

Nice hotel but there are things you can improve on.
Welcome scent on the room. Smells like old rag.
Window shades. It will be nice if I can access it quickly without fully rolling down the shades.
It is a really nice and entertaining hotel. All the restaurant are really good. The rooms are nice too
